comment._content: The picture shows a Friedrichshafen FF 49c in Swedish Navy service with Navy code '26'. Sweden bought two FF 49c direct from Friedrichshafen in January 1919 which obtained Navy codes '23' and '24'. They lasted till 1924 when written off. Two other FF 49c planes were taken into the Navy military operation as '25' and '26'. More information and pictures of the Swedish Navy operated FF 49c seaplanes can be seen at www.avrosys.nu/aircraft/MFV/057ff49c/57FF49C.htm
